text: Blaire (born June 6, 1994), known online as QTCinderella, is an American Twitch streamer, internet personality, YouTuber, and podcaster. She is the creator and host of The Streamer Awards. She is also a co-host of the Wine About It podcast and the Fear& podcast. Blaire was born on June 6, 1994, and grew up in Washington. Blaire also played Cinderella at Disneyland for a short time, which is where her streamer name came from. Blaire began dating streamer Ludwig Ahgren in early 2020. They currently live together in Los Angeles, California.
